WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:47.001 --> 02:49.045
<font color="#D900D9">(MAN PRAYING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)</font>

02:54.968 --> 02:56.302
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>

02:57.011 --> 02:59.222
<font color="#D900D9">(CONTINUES SPEAKING IN FOREIGN
LANGUAGE)</font> <font color="#D900D9">(WOMEN WEEPING)</font>

03:26.082 --> 03:27.333
He slaughtered our men...

03:29.377 --> 03:30.545
our brothers...

03:32.797 --> 03:33.923
our sons.

03:34.007 --> 03:35.133
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

03:36.467 --> 03:39.888
The dead cry out
to us for justice.

03:40.763 --> 03:44.225
On their souls, I swear to you.

03:44.976 --> 03:48.313
The man who took
our loved ones from us...

03:48.479 --> 03:52.525
the man who has brought us
such pain and sorrow.

03:54.068 --> 03:55.820
We Will find him.

03:56.738 --> 03:58.698
We will bring him here.

04:00.617 --> 04:06.372
We will not rest until his blood
flows into this very ground.

04:08.374 --> 04:10.877
We will have our revenge.

04:20.053 --> 04:21.678
<font color="#D900D9">(JAZZY MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

04:32.649 --> 04:34.108
Sir? Excuse me.

04:34.275 --> 04:35.485
Yeah.

04:36.027 --> 04:38.404
The finish is included
in the cost of the wash.

04:38.571 --> 04:40.782
That's okay,
I'd rather do it myself.

04:40.865 --> 04:43.576
I'm a little
obsessive that way.

05:25.034 --> 05:26.786
Lenore.
Bryan.

05:26.953 --> 05:27.996
Hi. How are you?

05:28.162 --> 05:29.330
Fine. You?

05:29.414 --> 05:31.082
Mmm, good, good.

05:31.416 --> 05:32.250
Is something up?

05:32.417 --> 05:35.003
No. It's Saturday, two o'clock.

05:35.169 --> 05:37.046
Kim's driving lesson?

05:37.213 --> 05:38.881
Uh... Music lesson
got switched.

05:39.048 --> 05:41.259
The Tuesday one
or the Friday one?

05:41.426 --> 05:43.344
I have no idea.

05:43.428 --> 05:44.721
<font color="#D900D9">(BOTH CHUCKLING)</font>

05:44.804 --> 05:46.264
You know how kids are.
Mmm-hmm.

05:46.431 --> 05:48.016
Especially the ones
who are desperate

05:48.099 --> 05:49.819
to pass their driving
test at the third try.

05:49.934 --> 05:50.935
She's not desperate.

05:51.102 --> 05:54.897
But she failed the test twice, Lennie.
It's important.

05:55.064 --> 05:58.192
So, where is she, really?

05:59.694 --> 06:01.404
I've never been
a good liar, have I?

06:01.571 --> 06:03.531
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>
No, it's not your forte.

06:05.450 --> 06:07.785
She's at her boyfriend.

06:11.330 --> 06:13.291
She has a boyfriend?

06:13.458 --> 06:15.334
Do you want to
come in for a drink?

06:16.044 --> 06:17.462
Yeah.
I think you should.

06:21.257 --> 06:23.458
Why didn't she tell me, for God's sake?
<font color="#D900D9">(LENORE SIGHING)</font>

06:23.468 --> 06:25.868
She probably didn't want you
running a full security check...

06:25.928 --> 06:28.765
of everything he's done
since kindergarten.

06:32.310 --> 06:34.228
But she's okay, right?

06:34.395 --> 06:35.354
Yeah, she's okay.

06:40.568 --> 06:44.405
Lennie, tell me
it's none of my business...

06:44.572 --> 06:46.365
but are you okay?

06:47.408 --> 06:48.576
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

06:48.701 --> 06:49.702
No.

06:50.828 --> 06:52.497
Not really.

06:52.663 --> 06:54.832
We've separated.

06:56.918 --> 06:59.796
Lennie, if there's
anything I can do...

07:01.089 --> 07:02.673
Well, I better...

07:02.965 --> 07:04.550
Thanks for the wine.

07:05.510 --> 07:06.260
Bryan.

07:07.220 --> 07:07.929
Don't.

07:08.304 --> 07:09.514
I don't even know
where the kid lives.

07:09.680 --> 07:14.060
You found her in a city of 12
million people within 72 hours.

07:14.227 --> 07:15.103
Promise me.

07:15.269 --> 07:16.979
I just told you...
Promise.

07:17.772 --> 07:19.941
I'm going to
give her her space.

07:25.363 --> 07:28.366
<i>Let me show you what I know</i>

07:28.616 --> 07:29.659
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE BUZZING)</font>

07:29.742 --> 07:33.120
<i>Let me take you where I'll go</i>

07:34.330 --> 07:37.667
<i>I want to, yeah, share with you</i>

07:38.793 --> 07:41.045
<i>Why won't you let me...</i>

07:41.212 --> 07:43.256
Um... Just wait a sec.

07:43.422 --> 07:44.465
What?

07:49.053 --> 07:50.555
I really like you.

07:52.056 --> 07:53.057
What is it?

07:54.392 --> 07:57.562
Um...
It's okay. It's okay.

07:58.896 --> 08:00.189
Take all the time you need.

08:05.403 --> 08:08.489
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE BUZZING)</font>

08:15.830 --> 08:17.039
<font color="#D900D9">(RINGING DOORBELL)</font>

08:23.087 --> 08:24.213
Hi.

08:25.590 --> 08:27.174
May I help you?

08:29.594 --> 08:31.429
Is Kim here?
Yeah, and you are...?

08:31.596 --> 08:32.679
Her father.

08:33.264 --> 08:36.100
Mr. Mills, what a pleasure.
I'm Jamie.

08:37.559 --> 08:39.061
Come in.

08:41.522 --> 08:43.065
Can I get you anything?
A drink?

08:43.232 --> 08:44.901
Just my daughter will be fine.

08:46.068 --> 08:46.944
Dad?

08:47.111 --> 08:48.112
Hi.

08:48.279 --> 08:49.447
What are you doing here?

08:49.614 --> 08:51.866
I know how important it is
for you to pass your test.

08:52.450 --> 08:53.951
Wait. Kim, you don't
have a license?

08:54.118 --> 08:55.745
Have you ever tried to
parallel park an Escalade?

08:55.912 --> 08:58.289
I told you to take
the test with my car.

08:58.456 --> 08:59.624
God. Dad.

09:03.794 --> 09:04.754
Thank you.

09:06.255 --> 09:08.132
A pleasure to
meet you, Mr. Mills.

09:16.057 --> 09:18.809
<font color="#808080">BRYAN:</font> <i> Could we slow down
a little bit, please?</i>

09:19.143 --> 09:21.228
I can't believe you just did that.
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

09:21.646 --> 09:23.314
You're leaving on
fall break next week.

09:23.481 --> 09:26.442
This is the only time I can get to
do this before I go to Istanbul.

09:26.609 --> 09:28.653
<i>We planned this. When you
make plans, you keep them.</i>

09:28.819 --> 09:30.237
No, Dad, you planned this.

09:31.447 --> 09:32.657
How did you even find me?

09:32.823 --> 09:33.944
Your mom and I were talking.

09:33.950 --> 09:35.284
Why didn't you tell me
you have a boyfriend?

09:35.451 --> 09:36.744
Because I knew
you'd overreact...

09:36.911 --> 09:39.956
and I just want to feel normal
even if I'm just pretending.

09:40.623 --> 09:42.249
Remember to brake
before the stop...

09:42.416 --> 09:43.000
Dad.

09:47.838 --> 09:50.257
Mom doesn't know
where Jamie lives.

09:52.677 --> 09:53.719
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

09:53.803 --> 09:55.137
GPS?

09:55.304 --> 09:58.516
I had it installed in your phone.
I'm sorry.

09:58.683 --> 10:01.852
You hear so many scary stories of
goings-on with people your age...

10:02.019 --> 10:04.339
Dad, I don't even know how to
start feeling normal again...

10:04.355 --> 10:05.690
but this definitely isn't it.

10:07.984 --> 10:09.610
Kim, you can move.

10:22.665 --> 10:24.625
Use your side mirror.

10:37.221 --> 10:40.558
Perfect. Why couldn't you
do that in the test?

10:41.225 --> 10:42.393
I don't know.

10:42.560 --> 10:45.062
Maybe I didn't really
want a license.

10:45.229 --> 10:46.230
Listen...

10:46.397 --> 10:49.025
of course I know
where you're coming from.

10:49.191 --> 10:51.736
But you have to trust me
to figure this out.

10:52.695 --> 10:55.072
Don't do this again, please?

10:55.239 --> 10:56.490
I won't.

10:57.074 --> 11:00.161
And don't go running a background
check on him with your friends.

11:00.327 --> 11:01.662
I won't.

11:03.497 --> 11:04.331
Okay.

11:04.498 --> 11:06.333
See you Wednesday.

11:06.500 --> 11:07.877
Two o'clock.

11:08.836 --> 11:09.712
Love you.

11:09.879 --> 11:12.089
Hey, I love you.

11:36.781 --> 11:37.990
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGING)</font>

11:39.283 --> 11:40.284
Yeah.

11:40.367 --> 11:41.911
Sam. Hi. It's me.

11:42.745 --> 11:46.457
Listen. I want you to run a
check on someone. Jamie Conrad.

11:46.540 --> 11:48.167
The usual.
Not too deep.

11:48.334 --> 11:49.335
You got it.

11:49.543 --> 11:50.544
<i>Okay. Thanks.</i>

12:04.767 --> 12:05.810
<font color="#D900D9">(SPEAKING FRENCH)</font>

12:06.143 --> 12:06.644
Sir.

12:06.936 --> 12:07.937
Thank you.

12:14.026 --> 12:15.319
Mr. Pitrel?

12:15.861 --> 12:17.863
I have a registered letter for you.

12:18.155 --> 12:20.658
- Can you take that up, Sébastien?
- Yes, sir.

12:24.120 --> 12:24.829
Here.

12:28.791 --> 12:30.000
Sébastien?

12:45.933 --> 12:46.934
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

12:47.560 --> 12:48.644
<font color="#D900D9">(SPITTING)</font>

12:54.567 --> 12:55.568
Where is he?

12:56.026 --> 12:57.027
I told you.

12:59.196 --> 13:00.698
I don't know.

13:15.004 --> 13:16.088
Where is he?

13:19.592 --> 13:20.759
Where is he?

13:25.472 --> 13:26.640
Okay.

13:29.643 --> 13:30.811
<font color="#D900D9">(PANTING)</font>

13:31.562 --> 13:32.771
You want to play with me.

13:33.397 --> 13:34.440
No, no!

13:35.608 --> 13:37.067
<font color="#D900D9">(CRYING OUT IN PAIN)</font>

13:41.030 --> 13:42.615
But I'm a good player, too.

13:43.824 --> 13:45.159
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED SCREAMING)</font>

13:50.497 --> 13:51.582
Shh!

13:56.128 --> 13:57.004
Look.

13:57.296 --> 13:58.589
<font color="#808080">PITREL:</font> No, no!

14:00.257 --> 14:03.761
I guess the rules are changing.

14:06.764 --> 14:08.557
This man came to Paris.

14:09.475 --> 14:13.312
He used a card
to come into our house

14:13.854 --> 14:15.522
and kill my friends..

14:16.357 --> 14:17.358
And my brother.

14:23.447 --> 14:24.907
This is your card.

14:32.957 --> 14:34.124
Where is he?

14:35.709 --> 14:37.127
Where is he?
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED SCREAM)</font>

14:43.133 --> 14:45.219
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> Stu, where are you going?
Come back!

14:47.096 --> 14:48.180
<font color="#D900D9">(CAR ENGINE REVVING)</font>

15:21.338 --> 15:23.090
What's happened?
Are you okay?

15:23.257 --> 15:25.009
Yeah, I'm great.

15:25.175 --> 15:26.593
Come in. I'll get Kim.

15:26.760 --> 15:27.928
Hey, hey, hey.

15:29.179 --> 15:30.514
Lennie, talk to me.

15:30.889 --> 15:32.016
<font color="#D900D9">(SNIFFLING)</font>

15:32.141 --> 15:36.020
We had this trip planned to
China for Kim's spring break...

15:36.186 --> 15:39.189
as a family, to try
and work things out.

15:39.356 --> 15:40.858
And when Stu and I...

15:41.025 --> 15:43.235
I just thought it would
be nice for Kim and I

15:43.319 --> 15:45.112
to be away together...

15:45.279 --> 15:46.864
away from all the tension.

15:47.323 --> 15:48.699
He canceled everything.

15:49.033 --> 15:50.617
All the reservations.

15:50.784 --> 15:53.203
I just can't believe
he did this to us.

15:57.333 --> 15:58.876
I'm just so tired.

15:59.043 --> 16:01.045
Just the fighting, the lawyers.

16:01.211 --> 16:02.963
He's turned into
such a bastard.

16:03.130 --> 16:04.673
I'm sorry, Lennie.

16:04.840 --> 16:06.216
I'm sorry.

16:07.718 --> 16:10.387
I'm sorry. This is
really not your problem.

16:10.554 --> 16:12.848
It's my turn to have...

16:14.058 --> 16:15.351
I'll figure it out.

16:15.517 --> 16:16.977
Look...

16:17.144 --> 16:19.229
Why don't you and
Kim come with me?

16:19.897 --> 16:22.733
But we can't impose on you.
You're working.

16:22.900 --> 16:24.068
You're not imposing.

16:24.234 --> 16:25.736
I'm working for three days.

16:25.903 --> 16:28.155
Then you can come over.

16:28.322 --> 16:29.406
It could be fun.

16:29.740 --> 16:31.075
That's so sweet.

16:31.909 --> 16:33.994
I don't know.
I can't think right now.

16:34.161 --> 16:36.705
Sure, I understand.
No pressure.

16:36.872 --> 16:39.917
I leave in the morning.
I work three days. Call me.

16:40.084 --> 16:42.419
If you're coming, I'll hang around.
If not, I'll come back.

16:42.586 --> 16:43.587
That's it.

16:43.754 --> 16:45.214
I'll go get Kim.

16:45.381 --> 16:46.173
Okay.

16:46.423 --> 16:47.674
Thank you, Bryan.

16:53.931 --> 16:55.265
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

16:58.769 --> 17:00.187
<font color="#808080">SAM:</font> <i> She is
definitely coming.</i>

17:00.354 --> 17:02.523
I don't know. Sam, I don't know.
Oh, come on.

17:02.689 --> 17:04.233
You should have insisted.
Mmm-hmm.

17:04.942 --> 17:06.443
Come on, guys.
Cut me some slack.

17:06.609 --> 17:07.861
She's going
through a hard time.

17:07.944 --> 17:09.238
I didn't want to
make it harder on her.

17:09.405 --> 17:11.031
She was confiding in me.

17:11.115 --> 17:13.784
Oh! I didn't know you guys
were still so cozy...

17:13.909 --> 17:16.078
that she shares her
marriage issues with you.

17:16.244 --> 17:17.454
Wait a minute.

17:17.621 --> 17:21.040
I know you guys were close,
obviously, but are you close again?

17:21.208 --> 17:22.459
Close like...

17:22.626 --> 17:24.127
I'll lay money she's still
got something for him.

17:24.294 --> 17:25.796
Don't go there, friend.

17:25.963 --> 17:28.549
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font> Maybe he still
has something for her!

17:28.715 --> 17:31.301
Can we talk about basketball?
For God's sake, come on!

17:31.427 --> 17:32.761
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font>

17:48.318 --> 17:50.070
Istanbul.

17:59.413 --> 18:00.831
Thank you, Mr. Mills.

18:00.998 --> 18:03.667
You made my stay
feel very secure.

18:07.296 --> 18:09.590
Thank you.
Have a safe trip home.

18:09.756 --> 18:10.799
You also.

18:16.013 --> 18:17.347
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>

18:26.773 --> 18:29.443
<i>You've reached Lenore. Leave
a message after the beep.</i>

18:29.610 --> 18:31.320
Hey, it's me.

18:31.487 --> 18:32.863
No message from you...

18:33.030 --> 18:35.532
so I guess you probably
found some place to go.

18:35.699 --> 18:37.868
I hope things are
a little easier.

18:38.035 --> 18:41.163
If you ever need to talk
or anything, I'm here.

18:41.330 --> 18:42.789
I mean, I'll be there.

18:42.956 --> 18:45.792
I'll probably
ship out tomorrow.

18:45.959 --> 18:48.045
No news from Kim.

18:48.212 --> 18:50.297
I guess she's busy with
the boyfriend and all.

18:50.464 --> 18:51.548
Dad.

18:52.508 --> 18:53.592
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>

18:53.675 --> 18:54.760
Surprise!

18:54.843 --> 18:56.845
Oh, my God. Kim, baby.

18:57.888 --> 18:59.890
Hey, Lennie.
Hello, Bryan.

19:00.057 --> 19:02.726
I was just leaving you a message.
When I didn't hear, it was...

19:02.893 --> 19:04.061
We wanted to surprise you.

19:04.228 --> 19:05.812
Well, you succeeded.

19:05.896 --> 19:06.980
<font color="#D900D9">(ALL CHUCKLING)</font>

19:07.064 --> 19:08.425
You guys could have
been surprised.

19:08.482 --> 19:09.816
I could have been out
of here and headed home.

19:09.983 --> 19:11.401
Mom's been calling Sam.

19:11.568 --> 19:13.070
Oh, yeah?
Uh-huh. Yes.

19:13.237 --> 19:14.530
We've been tracking you.

19:14.696 --> 19:16.740
Exactly. You're not the
only one who's got moves.

19:16.907 --> 19:18.033
Apparently not.

19:18.909 --> 19:20.661
Welcome to Istanbul.

19:27.834 --> 19:29.253
Not too shabby, huh?

19:29.628 --> 19:30.462
Wow.

19:31.088 --> 19:33.423
Oh, my God.

19:33.590 --> 19:35.801
Mom, look at this.

19:36.510 --> 19:37.636
Oh, my God!

19:37.803 --> 19:38.804
<font color="#808080">KIM:</font> It's crazy, right?

19:38.971 --> 19:40.138
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> It's beautiful!

19:40.305 --> 19:42.266
Thank you so much.
My pleasure.

19:42.432 --> 19:43.793
Listen, I'll let you
get settled...

19:43.934 --> 19:46.144
and I'll come and collect
you in half an hour?

19:46.311 --> 19:47.604
Okay.

19:49.147 --> 19:50.941
Later.

20:09.209 --> 20:10.544
Good morning.

20:16.466 --> 20:17.217
Good.

20:17.884 --> 20:18.635
Go.

20:18.802 --> 20:19.469
Fast.

20:19.803 --> 20:20.554
Let's go.

20:42.034 --> 20:43.827
<font color="#D900D9">(NEWS PLAYING ON TV)</font>

21:07.809 --> 21:08.894
<font color="#D900D9">(DOORBELL RINGING)</font>

21:09.227 --> 21:10.270
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> Hey.
Hey.

21:10.437 --> 21:11.855
You look great.

21:12.022 --> 21:12.898
You, too.

21:13.732 --> 21:16.026
So, where are we heading?

21:16.193 --> 21:19.863
Well, I am going nowhere.
I'm beat.

21:20.030 --> 21:23.408
I'm just going to take a nice
long bath and get into bed.

21:23.575 --> 21:24.618
Lennie. Are you sure?

21:24.701 --> 21:25.702
Yeah.

21:27.245 --> 21:28.955
I guess it's just
you and me, kiddo.

21:29.206 --> 21:30.874
Anything special
you'd like to do?

21:32.876 --> 21:33.877
Kind of. Maybe.

21:37.381 --> 21:38.799
<font color="#D900D9">(DANCE MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

22:01.655 --> 22:03.198
Hey.
Hey.

22:04.074 --> 22:05.155
You ready to take off, too?

22:05.158 --> 22:06.993
No, I thought I'd stick around
for a couple of more hours.

22:07.202 --> 22:08.203
Really?
Yeah.

22:08.537 --> 22:10.580
Cool.
No. Just kidding.

22:10.747 --> 22:13.750
Come on. Let's go. All right.
It's so crazy here.

22:15.669 --> 22:21.925
On this side is Europe,
and the other side is Asia.

22:22.926 --> 22:26.513
And every conquest since,
for the last 2,500 years...

22:26.680 --> 22:29.933
whether it was the West going
East or the East going West...

22:30.100 --> 22:32.519
they all used this
very same waterway.

22:32.602 --> 22:33.854
<font color="#D900D9">(MAN SPEAKING
FOREIGN LANGUAGE)</font>

22:33.937 --> 22:35.814
You want some tea, baby?
Yeah.

22:35.981 --> 22:37.441
Just one, please.

22:37.607 --> 22:39.609
How do you know all this stuff?

22:39.985 --> 22:41.278
How do I know it?

22:41.611 --> 22:45.782
I read it in a book
on the flight over.

22:45.949 --> 22:48.285
And you can borrow
it if you wish.

22:48.452 --> 22:49.327
Yeah, I would.

22:50.787 --> 22:54.124
So, this Jamie...

22:54.291 --> 22:57.169
Is it... serious?

22:57.335 --> 22:58.795
That was a really
smooth transition.

23:00.046 --> 23:01.298
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>

23:02.048 --> 23:03.300
I don't know.

23:03.467 --> 23:05.135
It's only been a few months.

23:05.302 --> 23:07.137
Are you in love with him?

23:09.014 --> 23:10.807
I guess I'm not sure yet.

23:10.974 --> 23:13.351
Have you ever
been in love before?

23:17.022 --> 23:19.858
Not the way that
Mom talks about it.

23:20.025 --> 23:21.818
How does she describe it?

23:22.194 --> 23:24.821
She said when you guys met...

23:27.407 --> 23:29.242
that it was super special.

23:29.409 --> 23:31.203
Super special?
She said that?

23:31.369 --> 23:34.664
I think the exact
word she used was...

23:35.040 --> 23:37.000
"magical."

23:39.169 --> 23:41.171
Magical, huh?

23:41.338 --> 23:43.173
<font color="#D900D9">(FIREWORKS EXPLODING)</font>

23:52.057 --> 23:54.017
<font color="#D900D9">(MUEZZIN CALL TO PRAYER)</font>

24:25.549 --> 24:26.800
<font color="#D900D9">(GREETING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)</font>

24:27.884 --> 24:29.761
It's good to see
you again, my friend.

24:31.137 --> 24:32.847
<font color="#D900D9">(GREETING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)</font>

24:32.931 --> 24:34.266
Is everything prepared?

24:35.016 --> 24:36.393
As you requested.

24:37.352 --> 24:38.728
Ah! Perfect.

25:18.143 --> 25:19.686
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGING)</font>

25:21.438 --> 25:22.689
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE RINGING)</font>

25:23.565 --> 25:25.275
Yeah?
He's in the lobby.

25:25.442 --> 25:26.985
Wait until he's outside.

25:27.193 --> 25:29.112
And remember, alive.

25:31.364 --> 25:33.783
He's on to me.
I'm leaving.

25:50.800 --> 25:51.760
Hey<font color="#808080">.
BRYAN:</font> Hi.

25:51.926 --> 25:53.762
I thought we were
having lunch in the bazaar.

25:53.887 --> 25:54.971
Um...

25:55.055 --> 25:56.306
Jet lag just hit me...

25:56.473 --> 25:59.559
so I figured I'd veg out by
the pool and let you guys go.

25:59.726 --> 26:00.977
Meet up with you later?

26:01.645 --> 26:02.896
I guess. Okay with you?

26:03.063 --> 26:04.147
Of course. It's fine.

26:04.314 --> 26:06.107
Oh, okay. Bye.
Hey, Kim.

26:06.274 --> 26:08.394
That book I was telling you about?
It's on my dresser.

26:09.235 --> 26:10.070
Definitely.

26:10.236 --> 26:12.072
No adventuring.
I'll go call the car.

26:12.238 --> 26:13.323
Have fun.

26:14.074 --> 26:15.659
Hey, Kim.

26:15.825 --> 26:17.160
<font color="#D900D9">(SOFTLY)</font> I know
what you're doing.

26:17.327 --> 26:18.787
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font> What?

26:23.166 --> 26:24.250
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE RINGING)</font>

26:25.627 --> 26:27.003
Yeah?

26:27.170 --> 26:29.506
The daughter is staying here.
What can we do?

26:29.964 --> 26:32.801
I want all three of them.

26:33.510 --> 26:35.011
Yes?

26:37.263 --> 26:40.350
She thinks we just
fell off the turnip truck.

26:40.517 --> 26:41.559
What do you mean?

26:41.643 --> 26:43.269
She's trying to play cupid.

26:43.436 --> 26:44.437
Oh, I see.

26:45.021 --> 26:46.356
When you first came back...

26:46.523 --> 26:48.191
and said you wanted to
make up for all that time

26:48.274 --> 26:50.110
that you lost with Kim?
Uh-huh?

26:50.193 --> 26:52.821
I thought, "Right.
Three weeks, he's gone."

26:52.987 --> 26:55.532
That was usually about the
limit you stuck around.

26:55.699 --> 26:57.117
Give or take a week.

27:00.286 --> 27:01.287
Not too close.

27:01.830 --> 27:04.390
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> You really proved me wrong.
I thought you'd never change.

27:05.041 --> 27:06.042
Why not?

27:06.209 --> 27:08.503
I don't know.
Your personality.

27:08.670 --> 27:11.464
When you commit to something...

27:11.631 --> 27:13.049
you focus all
your energy there.

27:13.216 --> 27:14.551
Like a dog with a bone.

27:14.718 --> 27:16.386
Nice analogy.

27:17.220 --> 27:18.513
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>
You know what I mean.

27:18.680 --> 27:22.350
When you give, it's 100
percent of 100 percent.

27:22.517 --> 27:25.395
If I was on to something,
it was just that thing.

27:25.562 --> 27:28.231
Even though I tell myself
I should change...

27:28.398 --> 27:30.734
I could never give it up.

27:31.818 --> 27:33.361
You gave us up.
Mmm-mmm.

27:33.903 --> 27:35.864
No, never.

27:36.030 --> 27:37.907
Not in here.

27:38.032 --> 27:39.576
<font color="#D900D9">(POP MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

27:40.910 --> 27:42.078
<font color="#D900D9">(ELEVATOR DINGS)</font>

27:55.008 --> 27:57.427
Driver, turn left.

28:00.889 --> 28:02.599
Lennie, don't.

28:04.392 --> 28:05.268
What?

28:09.647 --> 28:10.927
Will you tell me
what's going on?

28:11.024 --> 28:12.025
It's okay.

28:17.280 --> 28:18.364
<font color="#D900D9">(HONKING IMPATIENTLY)</font>

28:18.823 --> 28:19.824
Where is he?

28:24.788 --> 28:26.989
You see the gallery entrance
in the middle of the block?

28:27.040 --> 28:29.000
Will you tell me what's going on?
Do you see it?

28:29.501 --> 28:30.502
Yeah, I see it.

28:30.668 --> 28:32.337
When we stop,
I want you to get out

28:32.420 --> 28:34.047
of the car like
you're a shopper.

28:34.214 --> 28:35.465
I want you to go inside.

28:35.632 --> 28:36.912
Will you tell me
what's going on?

28:36.925 --> 28:37.967
Listen to me.

28:38.134 --> 28:39.427
Lennie, there's
no time for this.

28:39.594 --> 28:41.221
Just talk to me!
Listen.

28:41.387 --> 28:44.140
When you exit the back of the
fabric store, turn right.

28:44.307 --> 28:45.975
Take the first
street on the right,

28:46.059 --> 28:47.685
then left on
the very next street.

28:47.852 --> 28:50.563
Go straight until you
come to a set of steps.

28:50.730 --> 28:54.025
There's a red corridor.
It's a lane.

28:54.192 --> 28:56.528
When you exit the lane,
there's a cab stand.

28:56.694 --> 28:57.946
Go back to the hotel.

28:58.112 --> 29:00.573
Get Kim. Get the head
of hotel security...

29:00.740 --> 29:03.451
and demand that he
cordon off your room.

29:03.618 --> 29:05.745
Do not open
the door for anyone.

29:05.912 --> 29:08.832
No room service, no police, no one.
You wait for me.

29:08.998 --> 29:10.583
I can't believe
this is happening.

29:10.750 --> 29:11.751
I need you to focus.

29:15.630 --> 29:17.006
Are you ready?

29:17.173 --> 29:18.049
No.

29:18.216 --> 29:20.218
I need you to be ready.
I need you to be ready.

29:20.385 --> 29:21.511
Come on, focus.

29:21.678 --> 29:22.804
Driver, stop.

29:24.639 --> 29:25.807
Okay, go.

29:25.974 --> 29:27.433
Wait, what about you?

29:27.600 --> 29:28.601
I'll be fine.

29:28.768 --> 29:31.088
It's the guys following us who
are about to have a problem.

29:31.187 --> 29:33.356
When a dog has a bone...

29:33.523 --> 29:35.804
the last thing you want to do
is try and take it from him.

29:41.447 --> 29:42.740
Be careful.

29:46.369 --> 29:47.245
Out of the car.

29:48.162 --> 29:50.748
Come on. Move,
move, move!

29:52.792 --> 29:53.877
<font color="#D900D9">(DIALING)</font>

29:54.252 --> 29:55.920
Sir! Please.

29:56.629 --> 29:58.298
Please. Sir!

30:01.426 --> 30:02.260
He knows.

30:03.136 --> 30:04.470
Do it now.

30:04.971 --> 30:06.055
<font color="#D900D9">(HONKING)</font>

30:23.698 --> 30:24.490
Come on.

30:24.574 --> 30:25.658
<font color="#D900D9">(HONKING)</font>

30:38.838 --> 30:40.173
<font color="#D900D9">(BUZZING)</font>

30:46.429 --> 30:47.263
Shit.

31:00.610 --> 31:03.112
Come on, Kim,
answer the goddamn phone.

31:27.637 --> 31:28.805
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOTS)</font>

31:37.105 --> 31:38.147
<font color="#D900D9">(CAR ALARM BEEPING)</font>

31:52.662 --> 31:53.746
He's gone!

32:05.508 --> 32:07.927
Oh, God, no!
Somebody help me!

32:08.094 --> 32:10.138
The key!
Open the door, please!

32:11.723 --> 32:12.557
Shit!

32:46.340 --> 32:47.425
<font color="#D900D9">(SPEAKING TURKISH)</font>

33:20.583 --> 33:21.584
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

33:28.257 --> 33:29.300
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font>

33:35.932 --> 33:36.974
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font>

33:59.664 --> 34:00.832
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

34:23.603 --> 34:24.730
I'll blow his brains out.

34:29.277 --> 34:31.362
<font color="#D900D9">(LENORE GROANING)</font>

34:31.779 --> 34:32.947
Oh, Bryan!

34:34.322 --> 34:35.157
Please!

34:35.658 --> 34:36.993
Drop the gun.

34:39.579 --> 34:40.830
<font color="#D900D9">(GIGGLING)</font>

34:40.996 --> 34:42.415
<i>I really wish you were here.</i>

34:42.581 --> 34:45.083
Me too. You have no idea.
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE BUZZING)</font>

34:46.502 --> 34:47.295
<i>What?</i>

34:47.962 --> 34:48.963
<i>My dad's calling.</i>

34:49.130 --> 34:50.422
<i>He's on a date with my mom.</i>

34:53.009 --> 34:54.260
I'll call you right back.

34:54.427 --> 34:56.178
<i>Miss you. Bye.</i>

34:59.307 --> 35:00.349
How's it going?

35:00.516 --> 35:01.851
Listen to me carefully, Kim.

35:03.686 --> 35:06.272
Your mother and I...

35:06.439 --> 35:07.940
are going to be taken.

35:09.483 --> 35:10.359
Daddy!

35:10.818 --> 35:12.028
Oh, my God.

35:12.194 --> 35:14.155
And people are going to
come for you, too.

35:14.447 --> 35:17.033
<i>Leave the place
where you are calmly.</i>

35:17.199 --> 35:19.160
<i>Go to where the book
is I told you about.</i>

35:19.327 --> 35:22.872
There's a door. Go into the
room and hide in the closet.

35:23.039 --> 35:25.041
<i>You got that?</i>
Yes.

35:25.207 --> 35:26.876
Good. I'll call you.

35:27.043 --> 35:29.545
Go, now.

35:30.504 --> 35:31.797
<font color="#D900D9">(BEEPING)</font>

35:36.677 --> 35:37.720
<font color="#D900D9">(GASPING)</font>

35:41.515 --> 35:42.391
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> No!

35:43.851 --> 35:44.810
No!

35:54.195 --> 35:55.071
No!

36:13.089 --> 36:15.549
She is in room 422.

36:16.258 --> 36:17.593
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> No! No!

36:17.677 --> 36:19.095
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED SCREAMING)</font>

36:30.606 --> 36:31.857
<font color="#D900D9">(FAINT TICKING)</font>

36:32.316 --> 36:35.277
<font color="#808080">BRYAN:</font> <i> One, two, three...</i>

36:35.444 --> 36:37.947
<i>four, five, six.</i>

36:39.740 --> 36:40.783
<i>Right turn.</i>

36:40.866 --> 36:42.243
<font color="#D900D9">(MUEZZIN CALL TO PRAYER)</font>

36:43.953 --> 36:45.246
<i>Man singing.</i>

36:54.672 --> 36:56.007
<font color="#D900D9">(TICKING)</font>

36:56.507 --> 36:58.968
<i>One, two, three...</i>

37:02.096 --> 37:03.305
<i>four.</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(SEAGULLS CAWING)</font>

37:03.973 --> 37:05.141
Boat.

37:15.109 --> 37:15.818
The pool!

37:26.662 --> 37:27.830
Security, fourth floor.

37:27.997 --> 37:28.998
<i>Do you copy me?</i>

37:29.498 --> 37:30.833
<i>Send someone now.</i>

37:31.542 --> 37:32.376
<font color="#808080">BRYAN:</font> <i>25...</i>

37:33.544 --> 37:35.671
<i>26... 27...</i>

37:36.839 --> 37:37.965
<i>28...</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(BOAT HORN BLOWING)</font>

37:38.924 --> 37:39.842
29.

37:39.925 --> 37:40.801
Stop.

37:49.018 --> 37:50.061
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE RINGING)</font>

37:50.853 --> 37:51.687
She's not here.

37:51.896 --> 37:53.856
- Not here?
<i>- Check her dad's room.</i>

38:05.618 --> 38:06.702
<font color="#D900D9">(BEEPING)</font>

38:20.925 --> 38:22.635
<font color="#808080">BRYAN:</font> <i> Hammer on metal.</i>

38:35.106 --> 38:37.525
<i>Left. Gear shift
to second.</i>

38:37.691 --> 38:40.277
<i>One, two, three.</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(TICKING)</font>

38:40.361 --> 38:41.403
<font color="#D900D9">(CHIRPING)</font>

38:42.196 --> 38:43.405
Birds.

38:44.532 --> 38:45.741
<font color="#D900D9">(PLAYING TUNE)</font>

38:47.076 --> 38:48.369
<font color="#D900D9">(CAR HONKING)</font>

38:48.577 --> 38:49.912
<font color="#D900D9">(DOG BARKING)</font>

38:53.415 --> 38:54.333
You have them?

38:54.500 --> 38:55.793
<font color="#808080">SUKO:</font> Yes, <i>efendi</i>. Both.

39:00.422 --> 39:01.590
Take them to the shop.

39:04.927 --> 39:05.970
<font color="#D900D9">(YELPS)</font>

39:24.780 --> 39:25.573
Look!

39:25.781 --> 39:26.740
A flip-flop.

39:31.954 --> 39:32.830
You go left!

39:33.038 --> 39:33.539
C'mon!

39:41.881 --> 39:42.923
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

39:43.382 --> 39:44.466
<font color="#808080">BRYAN:</font> <i>Right turn.</i>

39:44.633 --> 39:45.593
<i>Twenty-seven.</i>

39:46.302 --> 39:47.803
<font color="#D900D9">(WATCH CONTINUES TICKING)</font>

39:48.804 --> 39:49.638
<i>Stop.</i>

39:56.020 --> 39:58.022
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> No! No!

40:02.359 --> 40:03.569
<font color="#D900D9">(FOOTSTEPS)</font>

40:46.070 --> 40:47.196
I shot some guy!

40:55.746 --> 40:57.456
<font color="#D900D9">(EXCLAIMS)</font>
<font color="#D900D9">(ALARM RINGING)</font>

41:06.382 --> 41:07.549
<font color="#D900D9">(MOANING SOFTLY)</font>

41:09.718 --> 41:10.803
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING FAINTLY)</font>

41:21.522 --> 41:22.731
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

42:11.447 --> 42:13.073
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

42:18.287 --> 42:20.331
Come on, Sam. Pick up.

42:20.414 --> 42:21.457
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGING)</font>

42:21.540 --> 42:23.834
<i>Hey, this is Sam.
Leave me a message.</i>

42:24.001 --> 42:24.793
Shit.

42:29.631 --> 42:30.799
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE BUZZING)</font>

42:33.302 --> 42:34.470
Are you guys okay?

42:34.636 --> 42:36.972
No, no.
Are you all right?

42:37.139 --> 42:38.474
Yes.

42:38.640 --> 42:40.642
I'm just scared.

42:40.809 --> 42:43.187
Kim, listen to me
very carefully.

42:44.146 --> 42:46.648
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font> I need you to calm
down and pull yourself together.

42:46.982 --> 42:47.816
Okay.

42:47.983 --> 42:51.028
The men who came for you,
did they leave?

42:51.195 --> 42:53.864
Yes. What do they want?

42:54.031 --> 42:55.324
I'm going to find out.

42:55.657 --> 42:57.076
Is Mom okay?

43:00.329 --> 43:01.246
Dad.

43:02.164 --> 43:03.332
Mom's fine.

43:03.499 --> 43:04.666
<i>Okay.</i>

43:05.417 --> 43:06.835
What are we going to do?

43:07.336 --> 43:10.672
I want you to go to the U.S. Embassy.
You'll be safe there.

43:10.839 --> 43:12.424
What about you and Mom?

43:14.051 --> 43:16.762
I'll figure something out.

43:17.346 --> 43:18.389
Where are you now?

43:18.764 --> 43:20.391
I don't really know, Kim.

43:21.016 --> 43:23.060
<i>Dad, how can I tell them
where to find you, then?</i>

43:23.227 --> 43:25.020
You can't.
Now get going.

43:25.229 --> 43:26.105
No.

43:26.522 --> 43:27.356
Kimmie...

43:27.523 --> 43:29.441
No. Tell me what to do.

43:30.567 --> 43:31.402
No, Kim.

43:31.568 --> 43:33.445
Dad, if you tell me what
to do, I can do it.

43:33.862 --> 43:34.863
Kim, this is not a game.

43:35.030 --> 43:37.533
I know that.
It's my parents' lives.

43:38.700 --> 43:40.369
<i>Dad, please.</i>

43:40.536 --> 43:42.746
You're wasting time.

43:46.875 --> 43:47.876
<i>Please.</i>

43:48.210 --> 43:49.711
Tell me what to do.

43:51.213 --> 43:53.632
Can you get out of
the closet safely?

43:59.054 --> 43:59.763
Yes.

44:00.889 --> 44:03.809
If you can,
take the case with you.

44:04.893 --> 44:05.769
Okay.

44:17.072 --> 44:17.781
I'm out.

44:18.073 --> 44:23.454
The combination
is 23-28-84.

44:30.502 --> 44:31.670
<i>Is it open?</i>
Yeah.

44:31.837 --> 44:33.589
Okay. Do you see a map?

44:33.755 --> 44:34.465
Yeah.

44:34.631 --> 44:35.632
<i>Take the map.</i>

44:36.008 --> 44:38.260
You'll see a scale on
the top in kilometers.

44:38.510 --> 44:39.511
<i>Do you see it?</i>

44:41.597 --> 44:43.140
Yeah, I see it.

44:43.307 --> 44:45.434
Take a shoelace from one
of my shoes in the closet.

44:45.809 --> 44:47.686
<i>Use it as a guide.</i>

44:50.772 --> 44:52.107
<i>There's a pen in the case.</i>

44:52.274 --> 44:53.358
<i>Take it.</i>

44:54.651 --> 44:57.321
Draw a circle with the
hotel in the center of it.

44:59.490 --> 45:00.282
<i>It's done.</i>

45:00.449 --> 45:02.284
Make the diameter
three kilometers.

45:03.452 --> 45:04.495
<i>You got that?</i>

45:13.045 --> 45:13.879
<i>It's done.</i>

45:14.046 --> 45:16.006
Draw another circle with
the market in the center.

45:18.967 --> 45:19.551
<i>Okay.</i>

45:19.718 --> 45:21.637
Do the circles
intersect at any points?

45:21.803 --> 45:23.013
<i>No.</i>

45:24.681 --> 45:26.308
Now, take one of
those little cans,

45:26.391 --> 45:27.976
<i>the ones with
the pins on the top.</i>

45:28.477 --> 45:29.311
<i>It's a grenade.</i>

45:29.478 --> 45:31.980
I want you to go to the
balcony with the grenade.

45:33.815 --> 45:35.984
<i>Is there a safe place
you can throw it?</i>

45:39.696 --> 45:40.906
There's a parking garage.

45:41.073 --> 45:42.241
Anyone on it?

45:42.908 --> 45:43.742
<font color="#808080">KIM:</font> No.

45:43.909 --> 45:45.789
I want you to pull the pin
out of the grenade...

45:45.911 --> 45:47.496
<i>count to three
so I can hear it,</i>

45:47.579 --> 45:49.164
then toss it as far as you can.

45:49.331 --> 45:51.041
<i>And then run back
into the room.</i>

45:51.208 --> 45:53.919
Keep the phone on so I
can hear the explosion.

45:56.588 --> 45:57.422
One...

45:57.839 --> 45:58.674
<i>two...</i>

45:58.924 --> 45:59.591
three.

46:08.183 --> 46:10.894
One, two, three...

46:11.228 --> 46:12.521
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED EXPLOSION)</font>

46:15.023 --> 46:15.857
Dad?

46:16.024 --> 46:19.403
Now draw a circle on the map
with the hotel in the middle...

46:19.570 --> 46:23.031
and the circumference
at 4.5 kilometers.

46:30.038 --> 46:32.749
Do the circles
intersect at any points?

46:33.250 --> 46:34.793
Yeah, at two points.

46:34.960 --> 46:36.920
I'm at one of the two
intersecting points.

46:37.087 --> 46:40.799
Now go outside and look at
the flags on the rooftops.

46:41.633 --> 46:43.427
<i>Do you see the flags?</i>

46:45.220 --> 46:47.055
Yes.
Are they in the wind?

46:48.056 --> 46:50.058
Yeah.
Going east, right?

46:52.102 --> 46:53.562
I think so, yeah.
How did you know?

46:53.729 --> 46:54.771
Now look at the map.

46:54.938 --> 46:58.900
I want you to go to the point where
the circles intersect at the east.

46:59.067 --> 47:00.652
I want you to take
one of the guns,

47:00.736 --> 47:02.404
<i>get to a rooftop,
wait for my call.</i>

47:02.571 --> 47:03.905
And two of the grenades.

47:04.072 --> 47:07.993
Go to the rooftop at
the most easterly point.

47:08.910 --> 47:10.162
Get up to the rooftop.

47:10.495 --> 47:11.788
<i>Wait for my call.</i>

47:12.414 --> 47:14.750
Be casual, Kim.
Blend in.

47:15.167 --> 47:16.585
Okay.
<font color="#D900D9">(METAL CLANGING)</font>

47:19.087 --> 47:19.963
Dad?

47:22.424 --> 47:23.592
<i>Dad?</i>

47:25.093 --> 47:26.094
<font color="#D900D9">(BEEPING)</font>

47:31.099 --> 47:33.101
<font color="#D900D9">(PEOPLE TALKING INDISTINCTLY)</font>

48:27.572 --> 48:28.782
Who are you?

48:29.324 --> 48:31.618
Those clothes don't belong to you.

48:31.743 --> 48:32.869
Help!

48:33.328 --> 48:35.080
There's a thief in here!

48:40.544 --> 48:41.962
<font color="#D900D9">(SIRENS WAILING)</font>

48:52.681 --> 48:54.057
<font color="#D900D9">(DOOR OPENING)</font>

49:38.643 --> 49:40.395
You know this man?

49:47.402 --> 49:48.904
This one?

49:50.155 --> 49:51.156
This one?

49:52.240 --> 49:53.408
No.

49:54.493 --> 49:56.203
This one?

49:57.162 --> 49:58.163
What do you want?

49:58.330 --> 49:59.915
You recognize none of them.

50:00.081 --> 50:01.583
To you, they were nothing.

50:01.750 --> 50:03.919
But to other people...

50:05.086 --> 50:08.673
they are sons and grandsons.

50:09.007 --> 50:11.259
Fathers and husbands.

50:11.426 --> 50:13.428
And you killed them all.

50:14.930 --> 50:17.724
Like they were
so many nothings.

50:23.939 --> 50:25.899
<font color="#D900D9">(WHISPERING)</font> And this one?

50:27.442 --> 50:29.110
You recognize him?

50:29.528 --> 50:31.613
You do recognize him.

50:32.113 --> 50:35.450
Him, you didn’t just kill.
Him, you strapped to a chair.

50:35.617 --> 50:38.328
You attached electric
cables to the chair.

50:38.495 --> 50:40.372
You turned the current on...

50:40.539 --> 50:44.209
and you left it on
until his heart burst.

50:44.376 --> 50:48.838
He's the one who kidnapped dozens
of girls and ruined their lives.

50:49.005 --> 50:50.840
He was my son.

50:51.675 --> 50:55.095
Marko, from Tropojë.

50:55.929 --> 51:00.016
And I have come to
take you to Tropojë...

51:00.183 --> 51:03.812
to face you to the people
whose lives you have ruined.

51:03.979 --> 51:05.188
To give them justice.

51:05.355 --> 51:07.065
You mean to give them revenge.

51:07.232 --> 51:11.361
It if gives us peace
call it anything you wish.

51:11.945 --> 51:15.240
I killed your son because
he kidnapped my daughter.

51:17.534 --> 51:19.411
I don't care what he did!

51:21.371 --> 51:23.248
I only know...

51:23.415 --> 51:26.293
I will never see
his face again.

51:26.459 --> 51:29.004
I will never hear his voice.

51:29.796 --> 51:30.880
<font color="#D900D9">(KISSES)</font>

51:34.384 --> 51:37.304
And as you held him responsible
for your daughter...

51:37.470 --> 51:39.097
I hold you responsible for him.

51:41.057 --> 51:43.351
Your death will not be quick.

51:43.518 --> 51:45.186
It will not be pleasant.

51:45.353 --> 51:46.646
But before you die...

51:46.813 --> 51:48.607
this is what you will see.

51:49.649 --> 51:51.151
Bring her in.

51:55.030 --> 51:56.114
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

52:01.036 --> 52:03.038
Bryan...
<font color="#D900D9">(KNIFE CLICKS OPEN)</font>

52:10.545 --> 52:11.588
<font color="#D900D9">(CRIES OUT)</font>

52:14.883 --> 52:16.259
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED GROANING)</font>

52:24.351 --> 52:25.769
<font color="#D900D9">(LOUD GROANING)</font>

52:26.895 --> 52:30.523
How long will it take for the
blood to rush to her head...

52:30.690 --> 52:32.192
and have no place to go?

52:35.445 --> 52:37.697
About 30 minutes.

52:37.864 --> 52:40.575
You are right.
You're an expert for this.

52:40.742 --> 52:43.119
So you have 30 minutes
to watch her die.

52:43.286 --> 52:45.747
She had nothing
to do with this.

52:45.914 --> 52:47.832
Do what you want with me.
Let her go.

52:48.083 --> 52:49.751
Don't play the hero with me.

52:49.918 --> 52:51.836
Now we are going to
catch your daughter.

52:52.003 --> 52:55.256
She will be sold to the
lowest brothel in this world.

52:55.423 --> 52:56.883
<font color="#808080">LENORE:</font> No! No!

52:57.050 --> 53:00.345
She will be abused
by so many men...

53:00.512 --> 53:05.266
that she'll be nothing more than a
piece of meat a dog would not have.

53:18.863 --> 53:19.989
<font color="#D900D9">(LENORE SOBBING)</font>

53:20.073 --> 53:21.700
Don't listen to them, Lennie.

53:22.367 --> 53:23.368
Kim is safe.

53:23.535 --> 53:24.619
I spoke with her.

53:25.078 --> 53:26.329
She's safe.

53:26.663 --> 53:29.374
You have to stay calm.
Breathe slowly.

53:29.541 --> 53:30.542
You have to.

53:30.709 --> 53:32.877
I won't let anything
happen to you, or to her.

53:33.044 --> 53:34.087
I promise.

53:37.465 --> 53:38.633
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE RINGING)</font>

53:38.800 --> 53:39.801
<font color="#D900D9">(MEN TALKING EXCITEDLY)</font>

53:39.968 --> 53:41.219
<font color="#808080">MAN:</font> <i>Hello, Murad?</i>
Shh!

53:41.761 --> 53:42.762
Quiet.

53:42.929 --> 53:44.139
<i>We lost the girl.</i>

53:45.432 --> 53:46.474
The girl has gone.

53:46.641 --> 53:48.561
I'll be back as soon as
we get her, then we move.

53:49.227 --> 53:50.061
Come on!

53:50.603 --> 53:51.730
<font color="#D900D9">(LENORE GROANING)</font>

53:51.813 --> 53:53.148
Hold on, Lennie.

54:15.128 --> 54:16.796
Hold on, Lennie.
Hold on.

54:17.172 --> 54:18.381
<font color="#D900D9">(HONKING)</font>

54:22.677 --> 54:24.012
What's he doing?

54:25.680 --> 54:27.015
Get out of the way!

54:28.141 --> 54:29.809
Sorry! Sorry!

54:29.976 --> 54:32.103
Come back!
You have to pay!

54:35.148 --> 54:36.107
Lennie.

54:37.776 --> 54:38.693
Lennie.

54:48.203 --> 54:51.289
I'm with you, baby.
I'm here. I'm here.

55:15.230 --> 55:17.315
Come on. Call.

55:18.149 --> 55:19.734
Please, come on.

55:21.069 --> 55:21.861
Lennie.

55:22.028 --> 55:22.821
Bryan.

55:22.987 --> 55:25.073
Lennie. Lennie.

55:25.240 --> 55:26.825
I'm coming back.

55:38.670 --> 55:39.671
Please.

55:39.754 --> 55:41.130
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE BUZZING)</font> I'm here.

55:41.214 --> 55:42.257
Set off another grenade.

55:56.062 --> 55:58.273
<font color="#D900D9">(EXPLOSION)</font>

56:01.442 --> 56:03.152
Dad?
You're close.

56:03.486 --> 56:05.530
I want you to keep moving east.

56:05.697 --> 56:08.074
Count to 30 and then
set off another one.

56:08.241 --> 56:10.702
One, two, three...

56:14.998 --> 56:16.541
18,19...

56:19.627 --> 56:21.379
26, 27...

56:21.546 --> 56:23.548
28, 29...

56:24.090 --> 56:25.133
30.

56:26.843 --> 56:27.969
<font color="#D900D9">(EXPLOSION)</font>

56:31.222 --> 56:32.932
Go out and check
what's going on.

56:40.273 --> 56:42.108
Kim.
<i>Yeah.</i>

56:42.275 --> 56:45.653
Look east. Look for a
white cloud of steam.

56:47.655 --> 56:48.656
I see it.

56:48.823 --> 56:50.283
Run to it. Tell me
when you're there.

57:00.168 --> 57:01.169
I'm going down.

57:18.269 --> 57:19.979
Dad.
Where are you?

57:20.146 --> 57:21.147
I'm right by the steam.

57:21.314 --> 57:23.191
<i>Drop the gun down the vent.</i>

57:23.358 --> 57:25.026
Oh, God, they're here.
They're coming.

57:25.193 --> 57:26.903
Drop the gun, Kim, and run.

57:29.739 --> 57:30.573
Go.

57:30.865 --> 57:32.659
<i>Dad! They're coming.</i>

57:37.580 --> 57:38.873
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING ON RADIO)</font>

57:44.462 --> 57:45.880
<font color="#D900D9">(CHAIN RATTLING)</font>

58:05.900 --> 58:08.236
I'm coming back.

58:15.284 --> 58:16.661
<font color="#D900D9">(TALKING EXCITEDLY)</font>

58:40.101 --> 58:41.185
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font>

59:03.499 --> 59:04.667
<font color="#D900D9">(COCKS GUN)</font>

59:37.200 --> 59:38.326
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

01:00:00.848 --> 01:00:02.809
Drop that.

01:00:04.519 --> 01:00:05.436
On your knees!

01:00:09.273 --> 01:00:10.566
Don't do this.

01:00:10.817 --> 01:00:12.235
Please.

01:00:13.361 --> 01:00:14.529
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOTS)</font>

01:00:23.204 --> 01:00:24.914
Dad? <font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>

01:00:25.373 --> 01:00:27.500
Dad! Dad!

01:00:28.876 --> 01:00:30.002
Baby.

01:00:34.632 --> 01:00:35.633
Where's Mom?
Is she okay?

01:00:35.842 --> 01:00:38.553
She's safe.
She's safe.

01:00:40.555 --> 01:00:41.764
<font color="#D900D9">(WEEPING)</font>

01:00:48.563 --> 01:00:50.106
Slow down,
slow down, slow down.

01:00:53.776 --> 01:00:54.944
I've got a fare.

01:01:00.533 --> 01:01:01.367
I'll be back.

01:01:04.161 --> 01:01:05.371
<font color="#D900D9">(CALLS OUT
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE)</font>

01:01:10.418 --> 01:01:12.461
That man had the same
tattoo as the men in Paris.

01:01:12.628 --> 01:01:15.089
It's not you they want, Kim.
It's me.

01:01:30.688 --> 01:01:33.149
I want you to wait here.
I'm going to get Mom.

01:01:33.316 --> 01:01:35.443
Wait five minutes,
and if I don't show up...

01:01:35.610 --> 01:01:39.113
I want you to go straight here,
to the American Embassy.

01:01:39.780 --> 01:01:41.616
Tell them what happened. Dad...

01:01:41.782 --> 01:01:43.062
No time, Kim.
Give me your phone.

01:01:43.659 --> 01:01:46.495
You wait five minutes,
not a moment longer.

01:01:46.662 --> 01:01:49.165
No matter what happens,
time runs out, you go.

01:01:49.332 --> 01:01:50.666
You understand me?

01:01:51.626 --> 01:01:52.793
Okay.

01:02:24.492 --> 01:02:26.160
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING ON RADIO)</font>

01:02:40.508 --> 01:02:41.676
<font color="#D900D9">(MOANING)</font>

01:03:05.825 --> 01:03:07.034
<font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font>

01:03:25.928 --> 01:03:27.471
<font color="#D900D9">(LENORE SHOUTING WEAKLY)</font>

01:03:28.973 --> 01:03:29.974
No!

01:03:31.392 --> 01:03:32.226
No.

01:03:33.477 --> 01:03:34.145
Bryan!

01:03:51.120 --> 01:03:52.580
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGING)</font>

01:03:53.748 --> 01:03:54.582
Yes?

01:03:59.336 --> 01:04:00.629
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE BEEPING)</font>

01:04:03.924 --> 01:04:05.176
<font color="#D900D9">(METAL DOOR OPENING)</font>

01:04:21.150 --> 01:04:21.859
Move!

01:04:22.026 --> 01:04:23.778
You killed him.
I had no choice. Move.

01:04:23.944 --> 01:04:25.988
Where's Mom? She's
fine, she's not far.

01:04:26.155 --> 01:04:28.032
Where is she?
Come on, move!

01:04:30.618 --> 01:04:32.219
I don't want to do this.
Keep going, Kim.

01:04:32.286 --> 01:04:33.120
Where are we going?

01:04:33.287 --> 01:04:35.623
Go straight. We have
to go to the Embassy.

01:04:38.292 --> 01:04:39.502
I'm not sure I can.

01:04:39.668 --> 01:04:41.462
Do you know how to shoot? No.

01:04:41.629 --> 01:04:42.630
Then drive.

01:04:50.012 --> 01:04:51.388
They escaped.

01:04:54.141 --> 01:04:55.643
<i>Officer down in Balat.</i>

01:04:55.851 --> 01:04:56.560
Copy.

01:04:57.686 --> 01:04:58.521
Shit, cops.

01:04:58.646 --> 01:04:59.855
<font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font>

01:05:00.231 --> 01:05:00.981
I have to stop.

01:05:01.148 --> 01:05:03.317
No, I just shot one of them.
Now, go.

01:05:09.657 --> 01:05:10.741
<font color="#D900D9">(CRYING OUT)</font>

01:05:11.534 --> 01:05:12.660
Come on, go!

01:05:15.496 --> 01:05:16.747
<font color="#D900D9">(SIRENS WAILING)</font>

01:05:35.683 --> 01:05:36.725
Right.

01:05:42.022 --> 01:05:43.190
Back, back, back!

01:05:44.525 --> 01:05:46.026
Come on, move!

01:05:48.279 --> 01:05:49.446
Come on, Kim.

01:05:57.204 --> 01:05:58.455
Go, go!

01:06:00.124 --> 01:06:01.542
Faster.
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SCREECHING)</font>

01:06:05.212 --> 01:06:06.130
Keep going.

01:06:18.559 --> 01:06:20.102
Left!
Yeah.

01:06:22.605 --> 01:06:23.647
They're in the taxi!

01:06:26.567 --> 01:06:28.068
Keep going.

01:06:30.237 --> 01:06:31.238
Oh, no.
Shit.

01:06:31.405 --> 01:06:32.823
Stay low. Keep going.

01:06:37.328 --> 01:06:38.787
Come on, faster.
I can't.

01:06:38.954 --> 01:06:40.915
You can do it!
I can't!

01:06:42.625 --> 01:06:44.501
Come on, move! Move.
<font color="#D900D9">(HONKING)</font>

01:06:45.461 --> 01:06:46.587
Dad!
Keep going.

01:06:47.129 --> 01:06:47.963
<font color="#808080">KIM:</font> Move!

01:06:49.089 --> 01:06:50.090
Right.

01:07:02.144 --> 01:07:03.145
Oh, shit.

01:07:05.856 --> 01:07:06.857
No!

01:07:17.451 --> 01:07:18.535
<font color="#D900D9">(HONKING)</font>

01:07:29.129 --> 01:07:30.506
Come on, Kim. Move!

01:07:34.009 --> 01:07:35.260
Go!
I'm trying.

01:07:43.435 --> 01:07:44.520
Come on, keep going.

01:07:47.272 --> 01:07:48.232
Turn left.

01:07:55.864 --> 01:07:56.949
<font color="#D900D9">(SPEAKING FOREIGN LANGUAGE)</font>

01:07:57.616 --> 01:07:58.659
Shit.

01:08:00.244 --> 01:08:01.120
Dad!

01:08:01.286 --> 01:08:02.955
Keep going. Stay low.

01:08:15.718 --> 01:08:17.428
Faster, Kim.
I can't.

01:08:18.053 --> 01:08:19.263
<font color="#D900D9">(HORN BLARING)</font>

01:08:22.975 --> 01:08:24.268
Come on, faster!
Dad!

01:08:24.435 --> 01:08:25.769
Keep going.

01:08:29.273 --> 01:08:30.473
You can make it.
<font color="#D900D9">(HORN BLARING)</font>

01:08:31.774 --> 01:08:32.734
Do it.

01:08:52.712 --> 01:08:53.839
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SQUEALING)</font>

01:08:57.009 --> 01:08:58.510
Here! Don't stop.

01:08:58.676 --> 01:08:59.595
But the soldiers.

01:08:59.761 --> 01:09:01.013
They'll move.

01:09:01.846 --> 01:09:03.015
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNS COCKING)</font>

01:09:03.640 --> 01:09:04.390
Down, Kim!

01:09:21.533 --> 01:09:22.951
<font color="#D900D9">(ALARM BLARING)</font>

01:09:23.952 --> 01:09:24.995
<font color="#808080">MAN ON P.A.:</font> <i>Nobody shoot.</i>

01:09:25.287 --> 01:09:26.705
<i>It's a suicide bomber.</i>

01:09:31.001 --> 01:09:32.795
Are you okay?

01:09:32.961 --> 01:09:34.004
Yeah.

01:09:37.049 --> 01:09:39.343
Keep your head down, Kimmie.

01:09:46.850 --> 01:09:47.684
Hey, Bry.

01:09:47.850 --> 01:09:51.063
<i>Sam, we're in a courtyard of the U.
S. Embassy in Istanbul...</i>

01:09:51.229 --> 01:09:52.606
in a smashed-up car.

01:09:52.939 --> 01:09:53.774
<i>Don't ask.</i>

01:09:53.941 --> 01:09:56.235
Can you call someone to make
sure we don't get shot?

01:09:56.401 --> 01:09:57.444
Yeah, of course.

01:09:57.611 --> 01:09:59.071
<i>Thanks.</i>

01:09:59.238 --> 01:10:01.615
It's Bry. He's in
trouble in Istanbul.

01:10:03.867 --> 01:10:06.078
Mom didn't get away, did she?

01:10:08.539 --> 01:10:09.540
No.

01:10:09.706 --> 01:10:11.375
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font> Oh, God, Dad.

01:10:11.542 --> 01:10:12.835
Tell me the truth.
Is she...

01:10:13.001 --> 01:10:15.629
No, no, no, Kim.
No, she's not.

01:10:16.713 --> 01:10:19.925
But they have her.

01:10:20.092 --> 01:10:23.303
And they will use her until
they get what they want.

01:10:24.388 --> 01:10:25.180
Me.

01:10:27.766 --> 01:10:31.311
You'll be safe here in the
Embassy until I come back.

01:10:31.645 --> 01:10:34.064
Kimmie, it's going to be okay.

01:10:34.231 --> 01:10:36.358
Nothing's okay.

01:10:36.900 --> 01:10:38.902
Kim, listen.

01:10:40.988 --> 01:10:43.407
I have to find them...

01:10:43.574 --> 01:10:45.284
and bring your mom back.

01:10:45.450 --> 01:10:47.119
And then I have to
make sure these people

01:10:47.202 --> 01:10:48.871
never bother us
again in our lives.

01:10:50.289 --> 01:10:52.583
What are you going to do?

01:10:56.128 --> 01:10:58.088
What I do best.

01:11:05.512 --> 01:11:06.972
<font color="#D900D9">(KIM SOBBING)</font>

01:11:29.953 --> 01:11:31.496
Mrs. Mills.

01:11:33.207 --> 01:11:36.293
What should I do
with you, Mrs. Mills?

01:11:36.835 --> 01:11:38.629
<font color="#D900D9">(MUEZZIN CALL TO PRAYER)</font>

01:11:44.343 --> 01:11:45.761
<font color="#D900D9">(MUSIC PLAYING)</font>

01:12:35.227 --> 01:12:37.479
I have nothing against you.

01:12:37.646 --> 01:12:39.898
You didn't kill my son.

01:12:43.694 --> 01:12:46.863
But your husband did.

01:12:48.657 --> 01:12:51.410
Now, he betrayed
you by choosing

01:12:51.493 --> 01:12:54.496
to save your daughter
instead of you.

01:12:55.372 --> 01:12:57.916
He left you here like a dog.

01:12:59.876 --> 01:13:03.463
At least my daughter
is still alive.

01:13:06.425 --> 01:13:07.926
<font color="#D900D9">(MUEZZIN CALL TO PRAYER)</font>

01:13:19.980 --> 01:13:23.483
Mrs. Mills,
you're a good mother...

01:13:24.735 --> 01:13:26.737
and a brave woman.

01:13:28.238 --> 01:13:31.158
For that, I'm going to
send you back home...

01:13:31.992 --> 01:13:34.828
piece by piece.

01:13:38.915 --> 01:13:40.125
<font color="#D900D9">(SHIP HORN BLOWING)</font>

01:13:41.710 --> 01:13:43.045
<font color="#D900D9">(SEAGULLS CAWING)</font>

01:14:13.992 --> 01:14:15.118
<font color="#D900D9">(HAMMER TAPPING)</font>

